<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/liver-transplants-offer-new-hope-for-colorectal-cancer-patients-with-liver-metastasis/">Liver transplants offer new hope for colorectal cancer patients with liver metastasis</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
